  <name>IYERIS</name>
  <summary>A beautiful cross-platform file explorer</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      IYERIS is an alternative file browser for Linux, featuring a stunning 
      liquid-glass interface with smooth animations and modern design.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>File browsing with a beautiful interface</li>
      <li>File previewing for common file types</li>
      <li>File renaming, creation, and management</li>
      <li>Drag and drop support</li>
      <li>Cut, copy, and paste operations</li>
      <li>File properties viewer</li>
      <li>Basic theming support</li>
      <li>Favorites management</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Note: This is a side project and currently isn't intended 
      to be a full replacement for any file exploration application.
    </p>
  </description>
